    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The victory of the world is indeed not God's aim; therefore His own honour does not suffer that the world of which He has made use in order to chasten His people should for ever haughtily triumph. שׁמך is repeated with emphasis at the end of the petition in ",
